The sales by nine LWT directors made headline news when they were announced.
The sale was of more than 1m shares and raised Pounds 5.3m following the
conversion of management shares into ordinary.
The directors still retain considerable stakes in the company and have
undertaken not to sell any further shares without exceptional cause during
the course of the coming year.
Berkeley Group's managing director, Anthony Pidgeley, sold 500,000 shares at
431.5p. The group is involved in private residential housebuilding and
