for gearing of 37 per cent.
The preference holders can apply for shares on the basis of 10 ordinary for
81 of the 4.75 per cent convertible, 100 ordinary for 459 of the 5 per cent
convertible and one ordinary for nine 7 per cent convertible.
On the results the company said the first half had proved more variable than
anticipated, with the average room rate being affected adversely by
increased competition.
